{"tid":717390,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"［第一龍門］迪基亞世界盃數據令世人震驚","createTime":"2018-06-26T04:00:07.000Z","updateTime":"2018-07-01T16:49:06.000Z","uid":14075,"like":11,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":25,"replies":[{"pid":"fb11549b2a7e16ec90441b56b15f316b070b5b30","tid":717390,"uid":14075,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-26T04:00:07.000Z","msg":"The 27-year-old <span style=\"color: red;\">made his first save of the tournament in Spain&rsquo;s 2-2 draw with Morocco &mdash; an incredible 205 minutes into his campaign.</span><br />\n<br />\nPrior to that, <span style=\"color: red;\">De Gea had faced four shots and conceded four goals.</span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">He was the only goalkeeper at the World Cup to play two games and not make a single save.<br />\n</span><br />\nThe Spaniard ended his run with a diving save to deny Khalid Boutaib and will get more time to improve his record as his nation sealed progression to the round of 16.<br />\n<br />\nWhen Egypt goalkeeper Essam El-Hadary took to the field against Saudi Arabia, he made history.<br />\n<br />\nAt 45 years and 161 days old, El-Hadary broke the record for the oldest player to appear at a World Cup finals.<br />\n<br />\nThe Egyptian goalkeeper was two years and 158 days older than Colombian Faryd Mondrag&oacute;n, who previously held the record.<br />\n<br />\nHe was also older than three of the managers at the World Cup &ndash; Roberto Martinez, Mladen Krstajic and Aliou Cisse.<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d4547b2e521329a3db2a688fa70cadeb71d35f72","tid":717390,"uid":27652,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-26T04:08:53.000Z","msg":"廢龍<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bca45ff74797a9e6f26719b23cd76405009ae268","tid":7173